<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 22 - 31. Aedeagus, dorsal view of 22 Coptocarpus microps sp. nov. 23 C. erwini sp. nov. 24 C. cyllodinus (Fauvel) 25 C. amieuensis sp. nov. 26 C. magnus sp. nov. 27 Adelopomorpha tethys sp. nov. 28 A. tuberculata sp. nov. 29 A. glabra Heller 30 Adelopomorpha glabra group male from Mt. Koghis 31 Adelopomorpha glabra group male from Gelima." , "Figures 32 - 40. Aedeagus, left lateral view of 32 Coptocarpus microps sp. nov. 33 C. erwini sp. nov. 34 C. cyllodinus (Fauvel) 35 C. amieuensis sp. nov. 36 C. magnus sp. nov. 37 Adelopomorpha tethys sp. nov. 38 A. tuberculata sp. nov. 39 A. glabra Heller 40 right lateral view of tip with arrow indicating the dorsal tooth of C. magnus." , "Figures 41, 42. Dorsal habitus of 41 Adelopomorpha tuberculata 42 holotype of A. glabra Heller, with labels. Images of A. glabra by O. Jaeger, reproduced with permission from MTKD." , "Figures 13 - 16. Female reproductive tract, ventral view of New Caledonian species 13 Coptocarpus magnus sp. nov. (Me Maoya Camp) 14 Adelopomorpha glabra Heller (Mt. Panie) 15 Adelopomorpha glabra group type 1 female (Mt. Koghis) 16 Adelopomorpha glabra group type 2 female (Me Maoya Camp). Abbreviations: at, atrium; bc, bursa copulatrix; co, common oviduct; rc, receptaculum; sg, spermatheca gland; smc, seminal canal; spc, spermathecal canal. Scale bars: 0.5 mm." , "Figures 43, 44. Forebody, left dorsolateral view of 43 Adelopomorpha glabra Heller 44 Adelopomorpha glabra group male from Gelima." , "Figures 52, 53. Maps of localities of New Caledonian Oodini." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554056" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554057" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554054" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554051" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554062" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/554055" .

